\id HEB - Abureni 
\toc3 Iburu 
\toc1 A̠d̠ire Wa̠ U̠ge̠ U̠gi̠o̠m A̠nwunom Iburu Bho̠ 
\toc2 Iburu 
\toc1 A̠d̠ire Wa̠ U̠ge̠ U̠gi̠o̠m A̠nwunom Iburu Bho̠ 
\mt1 Iburu 
\imt1 Otighom 
\im O̠ni̠ wa̠ age̠ ma̠ A̠d̠ire a̠lebh onon na̠ omutiom d̠o̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ i̠pu̠r a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠na age̠ agi̠o̠m bho̠ e̠mar eloghom i̠na. A̠lebh onon bha̠ u̠ge̠ u̠gi̠om ogbo ibha̠ra̠nom ta̠ Akrai̠st, a̠nwunom A̠zu ya̠ na̠ e̠to̠ ma̠ omula̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ igba̠iny i̠ko̠lo̠gi̠ ogbo A̠zu bho̠. Ka̠din, ebula̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ awa ta̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠o̠ d̠a̠ amu̠gho̠nyan a̠gia̠ga̠i A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, a̠lebh onon a̠nwuna̠ nyen i̠kparakpar ibom a̠b̠utu a̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ omel o̠d̠u̠a (o̠we̠le̠man obha̠ra̠nom Akrai̠st o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi). U̠ge̠ unigha̠ nyen ogbo ya̠ na̠ ebha̠ra̠nom Akrai̠st. Ibha̠ra̠nom ma̠ A̠krai̠st ogbo A̠zu i̠nye̠n bho̠, kokpona̠ d̠o̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ i̠kparakpar ali̠gam a̠ruzu d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠nwunom, sekina̠ d̠a̠ ozu d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom A̠zu, na̠ a̠nwunom A̠rom. Akrai̠st ta̠ omula̠ d̠a̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠soroni ma̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠sora̠n od̠ighi agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ta̠ eloghom ma̠a̠ obha̠ra̠nom Akrai̠st ma̠a̠ ya̠ga̠i, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ Witenemeni bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠. A̠d̠ire a̠lebh onon na̠ a̠leriom ma̠a̠ obha̠ra̠nom A̠krai̠st a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ igba̠iny i̠ko̠lo̠gi̠ ogbo A̠zu. D̠a̠ kere kere e̠kal, bha̠ na̠ oleriom ma̠a̠ Akrai̠st a̠bhon a̠pu. A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st na̠ akpo̠ ma̠ e̠la omom i̠zo̠ bho̠, wa̠ a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ ugba̠i̠ny i̠zo̠ wa̠ ogbo A̠zu bho̠. Agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ od̠i bho̠, bha̠ i̠na a̠pu ma̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ A̠mozizi, sekina̠ rokur Ugba̠iny I̠zo̠ bho̠. D̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠na a̠rue ma̠ olelegi i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ na̠ adamaghan bho̠, na̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ ogbo id̠umom ta̠ Akrai̠st, ma̠ obha̠ra̠nom ibom a̠b̠utu releleguma̠ ra̠ anwani̠ na̠ ilobhiri ya̠ id̠umom ologi d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠ten, ya̠ isibhom id̠umom ologi d̠awa d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ali̠gam a̠ruzu. 
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ 
\io1 Agu̠o̠ Akrai̠st abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠ 4:1-16 Ib̠eb̠i a̠ghud̠um ogbo id̠umom ta̠ Akrai̠st \ior (1:1—3:19)\ior* 
\io1 Agu̠o̠ Akrai̠st abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠ \ior (4:1-16) \ior* 
\io1 Ib̠eb̠i a̠ghud̠um ogbo id̠umom ta̠ Akrai̠st \ior (5:1—8:13) \ior* 
\io1 Ogir okur ta̠ Akrai̠st wa̠ a̠peleni bho̠ \ior (9:1—10:39) \ior* 
\io1 I̠zo̠ wa̠ a̠bhon a̠pu bho̠ \ior (11:1-40) \ior* 
\io1 Ibom id̠umom ta̠ A̠zib̠a ya̠ od̠ud̠ul \ior (12:1—13:19) \ior* 
\io1 Ra̠kikiom ogbo id̠umom Akrai̠st ta̠ esibh ogir \ior (13:20-25) \ior* 
\io1 Ikpo a̠fugh ya̠ obhin okunigiom 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠ten, A̠zib̠a̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ a̠riwil bho̠ agba ma̠ a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar ma̠ a̠d̠izo igiel,  
\v 2 ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ekunuguma̠ i̠nye̠n, i̠na na̠ a̠bhin O̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ agba ma̠ i̠di̠ar na̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar. A̠zib̠a̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ O̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠, wa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eton eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar a̠nigha̠ bho̠, ale̠m eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar d̠a̠ a̠de na̠ e̠nai̠ny.  
\v 3 O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠mutioghom e̠b̠alab̠al isosorogia̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠le̠m d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠bhin ibom a̠limon o̠nu̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠sibh eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠ma ra̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ a̠guri. Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ i̠yar d̠a̠ i̠karabh bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon a̠pu bho̠.  
\v 4 O̠nyi̠ bho̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠d̠ien wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠ghol i̠na bho̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu ma̠ ita̠ awa bho̠.  
\v 5 D̠a̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, ka̠ oken wa̠ I̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠a̠: “Anwa O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠; anwa na̠ a̠ten O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ a̠didon.” Bo̠d̠o̠ sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ten O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠”?  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin o̠kpana o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ e̠ma ra̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Eb̠la̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ e̠ko̠l i̠na.”  
\v 7 I̠na agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ a̠tenemeni awa ma̠ itileduom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ aru̠mu̠gh, sa̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ re̠ba anya.”  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ O̠nyi̠ bho̠ sa̠ I̠na agba ma̠a̠, “E A̠zib̠a̠, a̠dila̠de irileghom d̠oyom ta̠ ad̠u̠a ma̠ id̠ud̠ul a̠ten id̠ud̠ul, sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠rileghom a̠nwunom d̠oyom d̠a̠ igielake̠.  
\v 9 Anwa a̠ba̠ra̠ ma̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala sa̠ i̠karabh na̠ eghir anwa ma̠ ologi. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom bho̠, aso̠n anwa a̠doni, a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠libhon ologi ya̠ id̠igh edim ipu ma̠ ita̠ ipa̠n ogbo.”  
\v 10 I̠na ab̠aram agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Anwa, Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, i̠le̠m a̠de bho̠ d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠, sa̠ ro̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ ogir a̠limon d̠oyom.  
\v 11 Awa ta̠ ekun, ya̠a̠ anwa ta̠ aro̠ kid̠ud̠ul. Awa ta̠ e̠ghu̠r eten igba̠iny ka̠ a̠rukpe ibura̠.  
\v 12 Anwa ta̠ a̠kporokpor awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ akapa, sa̠ ta̠ obhin awa onwegina̠ ka̠ a̠rukpe ibura̠ nyen. Ya̠a̠, anwa ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ ekunuguma ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ rala d̠oyom.  
\v 13 Orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aro̠ nyen ke̠re̠, ma̠ ola̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠a̠, “Ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ tu̠tu̠n ami̠ ta̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠oyom okpokpolom o̠gbam a̠sike d̠inyin.”  
\v 14 O̠ku̠a ka̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ka̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ eka̠? Awa aru̠mu̠gh, sa̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu ya̠ na̠ egir na̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ itenemeni bho̠. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, akpe̠ i̠yar o̠mar o̠nagha i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠yar umel o̠d̠u̠a.  
\v 2 Ezin bho̠ a̠duom wa̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ i̠gba imutiom bho̠ ya̠gia̠ga̠i, sa̠ na̠ osobh ase̠ ya̠ igielake̠ na̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠pi̠o̠gho̠m bho̠, na̠ iya̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠.  
\v 3 I̠yar ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠ omiza̠n ku̠gba ma̠ i̠yar oghel obom ogir itenemeni ola̠ o̠ku̠a? Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ a̠d̠ia̠ agba ma̠ ogir itenemeni onon a̠mutiom, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠ ibhin ra̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠yar ma̠ iya̠gia̠ga̠i.  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin relegh, na̠ ilologia̠n na̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ogir ilologia̠n, na̠ atu̠gi̠ re̠ne̠ghe̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, a̠muzoghod̠iom asu̠gbagba d̠awa d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\s1 Witenemeni bho̠ 
\p  
\v 5 I̠na na̠ onigha̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ma̠ orileghom e̠ma ra̠ a̠nwunom, wa̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠gba na̠ ogboloma̠ bho̠.  
\v 6 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, u̠gba ma̠ odi esi d̠a̠ ra̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “ ‘O̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ka̠ ere ma̠ ola̠ anwa na̠ aru̠ru̠an na̠ a̠gboloma̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ i̠na o̠nyi̠ ta̠ o̠ni̠ ke̠re̠ ma̠ ola̠ anwa na̠ a̠kponom’? 
\q2  
\v 7 Anwa i̠le̠m i̠na aki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠ki̠ra a̠pu ma̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ anwa ibhin eghoi isosorogia̠n na̠ edim izuom i̠na, 
\q2  
\v 8 iguri ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar d̠a̠ ekpukpu a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ orileghom.’ ” 
\p U̠ge̠ ma̠a̠, ‘eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar,’ o̠ku̠a na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ abar ola̠ usigimeni bo̠. Ya̠a̠, i̠yar ta̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ka̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ na̠ orileghom eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠se̠n.  
\v 9 Ya̠a̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠bi̠gh A̠zizo̠s wa, ekud̠i obhel sa̠ uguri ma̠ a̠dila̠de ola̠ aki̠r a̠pu ma̠ ita̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ d̠a̠ igbirigbir ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠na a̠gbika̠ a̠mugh ebula̠ i̠yar. I̠se̠n i̠yar na̠ o̠bi̠gh ka̠ na̠ ozuom i̠na ma̠ eghoi isosorogia̠n na̠ edim, d̠a̠ ebula̠ egbika̠ omugh d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 10 A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ ale̠m eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠, ato̠ ma̠ obhin a̠d̠izo anwi̠i̠ny od̠ighom d̠a̠ isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠. Sa̠ a̠bhon agu̠o̠ i̠na ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s amado̠n bho̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ egbika̠ ya̠ A̠zizo̠s atu̠n otenemeni awa a̠gbika̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠.  
\v 11 O̠ku̠a bha̠ i̠se̠n, A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠na na̠ ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a bho̠, na̠ eten anwi̠i̠ny onin eghun. Obha̠ ezin bho̠ i̠na od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l obhelegi awa ma̠ a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 12 Ezin bho̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠sen ib̠eb̠i ya̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien d̠oyom bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ da̠mi̠. 
\q2 Ami̠ ta̠ amo̠r aso̠r a̠tutumeni nyam d̠a̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n a̠nwunom bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 13 O̠lo̠gho̠m i̠se̠ sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Eb̠em ologi d̠ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” 
\p Sa̠ a̠mula̠ agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Ami̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n na̠ anwi̠i̠ny ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 14 Ebula̠ agu̠o̠ anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ asi̠ na̠ ipulupul bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ten o̠ni̠ ola̠ asi̠ na̠ ipulupul. I̠na a̠gir o̠ku̠a ma̠ o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ omugh d̠o̠yo̠ o̠pi̠e̠gi̠ a̠limon ta̠ Eru bho̠, wa̠ na̠ a̠sibh a̠limon omugh bho̠.  
\v 15 Ogir o̠ko̠no̠n a̠d̠ighi kisa̠ i̠na a̠rue a̠tenemeni ma̠ ogbo ya̠, d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠awa, i̠ro̠ ma̠ igoni d̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ omugh bho̠.  
\v 16 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i i̠na na̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun ta̠ Ebraham, ya̠a̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 17 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ u̠le̠m i̠na u̠gu̠b̠e̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ igbirigbir na̠ iya̠ igielake̠ aro̠ ma̠ We̠mu̠ Okur d̠i̠yar d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Sa̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ itulugia̠n na̠ okpon i̠karabh o̠si̠ghe̠ a̠d̠ien.  
\v 18 I̠se̠n i̠na na̠ a̠rue na̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠te̠i̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ a̠gbika̠ sa̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠te̠i̠ i̠na nyen. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, inyin a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, ogbo ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ab̠aram a̠bhelegi a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ e̠gi̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠. Iloghoma̠ne ma̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ i̠yar na̠ osen bho̠ ma̠a̠, i̠na wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ afi̠ri̠ma ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ ogir na̠ We̠mu̠ Okur ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠i̠yar bho̠.  
\v 2 I̠na a̠rugh ado̠l igielake̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ aso̠n i̠na bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ A̠mozizi a̠gir igiel bho̠ ub̠eton eb̠la̠ eghun otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ unigha̠ i̠na ma̠ orileghom bho̠.  
\v 3 Ya̠a̠, akpe̠ ma̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ A̠zizo̠s opu A̠mozizi, a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠lo ma̠ otu bho̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu ma̠ otu wa̠ i̠na a̠lo bho̠.  
\v 4 Ezin bho̠, eb̠la̠ a̠rutu ya̠ od̠i bho̠, o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠lo ma̠ odi i̠se̠. Ya̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ a̠lo kabar kabar.  
\v 5 A̠mozizi ob̠a̠ra̠motu ola̠ a̠rugh ya̠ igielake̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Ogir d̠o̠yo̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ elegh egboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ agba a̠mutiom d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠.  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, Akrai̠st a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de O̠nyi̠ na̠ a̠rileghom otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ igielake̠. I̠yar eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠ ku̠gba ma̠ i̠yar o̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠i̠yar, d̠a̠ abar wa̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠tu̠n na̠ obo d̠a̠ eb̠em ologi bho̠. 
\s1 Osira̠ epobh Anwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\p  
\v 7 O̠ku̠a bha̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ E̠mu̠gh Etu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Ka̠ inyin u̠mu̠gho̠n okoroko d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠didon,  
\v 8 o̠ni̠ ko o̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin agu̠o̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ id̠ud̠ul d̠inyin iwia̠n a̠limon ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ i̠d̠agi̠an i̠na d̠a̠ e̠ghana bho̠.  
\v 9 Awa i̠d̠agi̠an ami̠ d̠a̠ ebla̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ igir  
\v 10 d̠a̠ eruba̠l ala bho̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ ologi d̠ami̠ agam a̠nigha̠ ma̠ amu̠m obha̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, ‘Rologi d̠awa na̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an ipa̠n eb̠la̠ igiel, sa̠ awa na̠ e̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ i̠to̠ d̠ami̠.’  
\v 11 Sa̠ d̠a̠ i̠gam d̠ami̠, sa̠ ami̠ igurugia̠n ma̠a̠, awa ko o̠gi̠ d̠o̠ ka̠ ed̠igh ed̠e ma̠ e̠nu̠m d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh d̠ami̠.  
\v 12 A̠rumor d̠ami̠ na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, o̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni, o̠ni̠ inyin onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠karabh ologi na̠ ab̠agh e̠mu̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠.  
\v 13 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, odi akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi ta̠ odi ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠d̠a̠ma̠, d̠a̠ i̠to̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠karabh igelemeni ma̠ o̠ni̠ inyin ma̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ ab̠agh e̠mu̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 14 O̠ku̠a na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, eb̠la̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ od̠e ma̠ e̠nu̠m ogir ta̠ Akrai̠st, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠yar osibh o̠pu̠r ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠i̠yar o̠kparame̠ni̠, tu̠tu̠n ta̠ ate̠i̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠.  
\v 15 I̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ iya̠ u̠gba d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “Igiel inyin u̠mu̠gho̠n okoroko d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠didon, o̠ni̠ ko o̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ id̠ud̠ul d̠inyin, ma̠ igiel bho̠ awa iwia̠n a̠limon ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ igurumeni ma̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, wa̠ a̠nyen ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n okoroko ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ku̠ku̠m eka̠ sa̠ iwia̠n a̠limon d̠o̠yo̠ igurumeni ma̠ ologi bho̠? Eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ A̠mozizi a̠rileghom a̠mutiom d̠a̠ Izipt bho̠.  
\v 17 Wa̠ a̠nyen ogbo ya̠ i̠na agam i̠gam a̠nigha̠ ma̠ eruba̠l rala bho̠? I̠nye̠ ogbo ya̠ igir i̠karabh sa̠ imugughu, sa̠ regua̠de d̠awa i̠ro̠ i̠b̠o̠r d̠a̠ e̠ghana bho̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 18 Ya̠a̠, wa̠ a̠nyen ogbo ya̠ agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠gurugia̠n ma̠a̠, “Awa ko o̠gi̠ d̠o̠ ka̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh d̠ami̠” bho̠? Ogbo ya̠ i̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ inigha̠ i̠na bho̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 19 O̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠ agbo̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ awa oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa orue d̠o̠ ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh d̠o̠yo̠. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠sibh ogua̠n wa̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n ma̠a̠, i̠yar ta̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, i̠yar ta̠ okpona̠, b̠o̠ka̠ bebena̠ o̠ni̠ inyin na̠ o̠pi̠o̠m (omel ad̠u̠a) ma̠ ola̠ i̠na ko o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ a̠d̠igh.  
\v 2 O̠lo̠gho̠m i̠se̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n ani̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ya̠ u̠gba unigha̠ i̠yar bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠. Ya̠a̠, id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ asu̠o̠ enigha̠ awa ma̠ igiel bho̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa inwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ wa̠ o̠da asu̠gbagba bho̠ obhin.  
\v 3 I̠yar ogbo ya̠ na̠ oma̠ra̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠ na̠ o̠te̠i̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Ami̠ ibhin d̠a̠ i̠gam a̠gurugia̠n ma̠a̠, awa ko od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh d̠ami̠.” 
\p A̠zib̠a̠ a̠kunugiom o̠le̠m i̠di̠ar ka̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na alem e̠ma ra̠nwunom awe̠le̠ bho̠; ku̠ku̠m eka̠, i̠na agba ma̠ o̠ku̠a a̠mutiom.  
\v 4 I̠na agba ma̠ odi esi d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ oleghemeni od̠ua̠l a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Igiel bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ale̠m i̠di̠ar a̠kunugiom bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠sira̠ ma̠ epobh oleghemeni od̠ua̠l a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 5 D̠a̠ onin esi obha̠ sa̠ i̠na agba a̠numeta̠n ma̠a̠, “Awa ko od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh d̠ami̠.”  
\v 6 Agu̠o̠ na̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ idi ogbo ta̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh bho̠, sa ogbo ya̠ ud̠ia̠ u̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ unigha̠ bho̠ ko od̠igh d̠o̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ i̠we̠le̠ ma̠ o̠da obhin bho̠,  
\v 7 sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠nwe a̠gua̠n opa̠n a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ orue od̠igh. “A̠didon” a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠. D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠bia̠ ma̠ o̠gu̠man, sa̠ i̠na awo̠l d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ta̠ A̠devidi agba a̠mutiom agu̠o̠ i̠na agba ma̠ i̠se bho̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Ka̠ inyin u̠mu̠gho̠n okoroko ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ a̠didon, o̠ni̠ ko o̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ ma̠ e̠we̠le̠man o̠nagha.” 
\p  
\v 8 Aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠zosu̠a a̠rileghom awa ka̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh nab̠o̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ka̠ ifugh d̠o̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ onon d̠a̠ obhel o̠gu̠man.  
\v 9 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, na̠ oguri ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠-epobh osisa̠n a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 10 O̠ku̠a bha̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ e̠b̠e̠l a̠d̠igh a̠d̠e d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, o̠ni̠ bho̠ eka̠ ta̠ a̠gir ogir o̠yo̠ a̠sira̠ ma̠ epobh, ma̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gir bho̠.  
\v 11 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, owia̠n od̠igh d̠a̠ esi osira̠ epobh obha̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠e̠l, b̠o̠ka̠ o̠ni̠ i̠yar na̠ omugh a̠bhe d̠a̠ ebula̠ ab̠agh e̠mu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa.  
\v 12 Ezin bho̠, o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um sa̠ na̠ a̠lol, sa̠ a̠sibh a̠pu ma̠ ab̠e̠ge̠re̠ (ogidi i̠wal-aman). Sa̠ na̠ a̠gu na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ eloghoma̠n ozu na̠ e̠mu̠gh o̠ni̠, ma̠ o̠bagi̠o̠n awa d̠a̠ re̠tu̠tu̠la na̠ ali̠si̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠rue na̠ agba ma̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na i̠ru̠ruan na̠ i̠walama ologi.  
\v 13 Bebina̠ abar ola̠ u̠le̠m usoroni d̠a̠ a̠de onon, ola̠ awo̠gi̠na d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bo̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠, na̠ ob̠ugh kabarkabar omutiom e̠ma, d̠a̠ a̠misigh o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠gba ma̠ ado̠l d̠i̠yar onigha̠ bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s Obom We̠mu̠ Okur Bho̠ 
\p  
\v 14 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠kpaghano̠m id̠umom d̠i̠yar. Ezin bho̠, i̠yar onwuna̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, obom We̠mu̠ Okur wa̠ na̠ a̠bhun d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.  
\v 15 I̠yar unwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ We̠mu̠ Okur ola̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ okpon i̠yar igbirigbir d̠a̠ rasu̠nwe̠r d̠i̠yar. Ya̠a̠, i̠yar unwuna̠ ma̠ We̠mu̠ Okur ola̠ a̠d̠izo re̠kal ad̠agi̠an i̠te̠i̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ i̠yar i̠se̠n bho̠, ku̠ku̠m eka̠ i̠na na̠ omel d̠o̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ i̠karabh.  
\v 16 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, obhin d̠a̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠lukpesi e̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠yar o̠te̠i̠ okpon igbirigbir na̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠, d̠a̠ obhel i̠kparama ado̠l. 
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 Na̠ okpon d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ o̠so̠n ghan we̠mu̠ rokur, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na amara ma̠ eni d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ako̠l i̠ko̠l akpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ ya̠ otenemeni awa d̠a̠ i̠karabh.  
\v 2 Agu̠o̠ i̠na eka̠ na̠ a̠dugh a̠ludugh bho̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rue na̠ a̠bhin odudugha̠n ologi na̠ a̠kpon ogbo ya̠ ologhoma̠n d̠o̠ sa̠ na̠ egir i̠karabh bho̠.  
\v 3 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ akpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 4 O̠ni̠ ola̠ i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ a̠rue ate̠i̠ a̠d̠ien a̠dila̠de edim onon bo̠, a̠ten ka̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhelegi i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ Ero̠n bho̠.  
\v 5 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ Akrai̠st na̠ agu̠o̠ o̠re̠ma d̠o̠ ma̠ alu̠bu̠gh a̠ten we̠mu̠ rokur. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ka̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠. Ob̠eton a̠didon, ami̠ na̠ a̠ten o̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom.”  
\v 6 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba ma̠ opa̠n esi ma̠a̠, “Anwa okur ola̠ ta̠ aro̠ tu̠tu̠n ka̠ id̠ud̠ul, ola̠ a̠d̠ien e̠mar ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ta̠ Ame̠lki̠ze̠de̠k.  
\v 7 D̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom, i̠na a̠siseiny a̠siseiny, a̠puru ma̠ okpon igbirigbir, a̠leghe ma̠ ed̠i agba ma̠ igbir a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon otenemeni o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠. Sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ awo̠ran i̠na d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ o̠zu igielake̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 8 Ebla̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ Onyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ eka̠, i̠na a̠bhin egbika̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠gbika̠ bho̠ atu̠ghan o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ o̠zu.  
\v 9 Igiel bho̠ na̠ o̠b̠ab̠a̠le̠ni̠ i̠na o̠mado̠n bho̠, sa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ eten wa̠ ogbo ya̠ id̠umom i̠na ta̠ e̠wol e̠te̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um ka̠ id̠ud̠ul bho̠.  
\v 10 Sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠guri i̠na ma̠ a̠dila̠de we̠mu̠ rokur, ola̠ a̠d̠ien e̠mar ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ta̠ Ame̠lki̠ze̠de̠k.  
\v 11 I̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠gba ogboloma̠ o̠yo̠ a̠b̠utu, ya̠a̠ ta̠ akpar ogba o̠si̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ onigha̠ inyin, ezin bho̠ i̠nyin na̠ o̠b̠o̠ri̠o̠m o̠mu̠gho̠nyan abar.  
\v 12 Obhel amar aro̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin oten ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n, ya̠a̠ od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ ola̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin i̠pu̠r ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar imutuma̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. O̠ku̠a̠ bha̠ inyin na̠ oten ogbo ya̠ ta̠ onigha̠ amu̠mam amu̠mam, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n.  
\v 13 Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ amam amu̠mam od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠, ola̠ ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala.  
\v 14 Ya̠a̠, ikpo ed̠ia̠n i̠ro̠ inigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠ikighu ma̠ aru̠mu̠, ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠ghan e̠ku̠ro̠m sa̠ na̠ erue na̠ eloghom a̠nwegia̠n ta̠ i̠karabh na̠ ib̠eb̠i. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni, owia̠n eloghom abar d̠i̠yar d̠a̠ Akrai̠st a̠pel ya̠ i̠yar u̠tu̠ghan d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠. Omula̠ d̠o̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de ola̠ na̠ a̠puru ma̠ okpon i̠karabh o̠si̠ghe̠ a̠d̠ien, d̠a̠ ebula̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar ya̠ eb̠em ologi o̠to̠ d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠;  
\v 2 na̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ozu, na̠ o̠gbamagi̠ aru̠gu̠o̠, na̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh, na̠ ebhum ase̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ bho̠.  
\v 3 Akpe̠ i̠yar ogir o̠ku̠a, d̠a̠ okpon igbirigbir ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 4 Ta̠ akpar ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠ia̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠alab̠al bho̠ e̠d̠e̠d̠i̠ma ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ote̠nai̠ny, sa̠ id̠e̠d̠ia̠n na̠ Ob̠eb̠i E̠mu̠gh bho̠,  
\v 5 e̠bi̠gh e̠no̠gho̠man o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ ra̠limon amu̠m wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠,  
\v 6 ma̠ orue otiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh ku̠gba ma̠ awa emel e̠d̠u̠a. O̠ku̠a bha̠ awa na̠ enwe na̠ egigh o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠, na̠ e̠lo̠gi̠ i̠na ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l na̠ emutiom e̠ma.  
\v 7 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ a̠de wa̠ na̠ a̠mibh gha̠n amu̠m o̠lo̠bha wa̠ na̠ a̠ba̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠bho̠m o̠yo̠ bho̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠b̠om ib̠eb̠i ed̠ia̠n na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ igbebh bho̠.  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠, a̠de ola̠ a̠d̠igh ib̠ub̠ulom na̠ ralai̠-agbo̠gi̠ri̠ bha̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠ a̠de, ola̠ na̠ orogi sa̠ ta̠ o̠bhu̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠.  
\v 9 Ib̠eb̠i ra̠tologha̠n d̠i̠yar, eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠i̠yar aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a bho̠ eka̠, i̠yar uma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ inyin ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ ibom e̠no̠gho̠man ya̠ uguri usisa̠n ogbo ya̠ na̠ otenemeni bho̠.  
\v 10 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ ipa̠n a̠gir ipa̠n. I̠na ko oweleta̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir d̠inyin, na̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ obhin na̠ otula̠n a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ma̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠lo̠gh na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ogbo-ogir d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, sa̠ inyin od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ ogir o̠ku̠a bho̠.  
\v 11 Na̠ ebhir i̠yar o̠bi̠gh ma̠a̠, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ inyin na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ onin onyen ologi bho̠ na̠ a̠gir ya̠ o̠te̠i̠ imuzoghod̠iom eb̠em ologi d̠o̠yo̠ tu̠tu̠n ekunuguma̠ bho̠.  
\v 12 I̠yar u̠bho̠ro̠gh d̠o̠ inyin o̠gbu̠o̠r, ya̠a̠ i̠ta ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ibhin d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ na̠ a̠ma̠ne i̠te̠i̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ ugua̠n uguri bho̠. 
\s1 Ogua̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠mite bho̠ 
\p  
\v 13 Igiel bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Ebraham bho̠, i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ a̠sibhigha̠n d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠pu i̠na o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ bho̠,  
\v 14 agba ma̠a̠, “D̠a̠ itutumeni, ami̠ ta̠ a̠tutumeni nyam ga̠i, d̠a̠ i̠mara sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ o̠la anwa ta̠ amaragi̠an a̠b̠utu anwi̠i̠ny.  
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ne a̠b̠ara̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ abar wa̠ uguan unigha̠ i̠na bho̠.  
\v 16 A̠nwunom na̠ ebhin a̠d̠ien o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠pu awa na̠ esibhigha̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ raku̠anan d̠awa na̠ ekun agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠zo̠ bho̠ ta̠ amara.  
\v 17 A̠zib̠a̠ abho̠ro̠gh o̠mar oleriom ogbo ya̠ ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ abar wa̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠, ma̠ i̠na na̠ onwe gha̠n o̠nu̠ d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠d̠ia̠n i̠zo̠ alo̠gho̠m.  
\v 18 A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠, ta̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ i̠wal i̠di̠ar ya̠ onwegia̠n gha̠n sa̠ i̠mara ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ igunugha̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, akpe̠ i̠yar ogbo ya̠ na̠ od̠igh ed̠oghotu d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ma̠ osibh abar eb̠em ologi wa̠ uguri usisa̠n i̠yar bho̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠.  
\v 19 Eb̠em ologi onon wa̠ i̠yar unwuna̠ bho̠, bha̠ a̠limon wa̠ na̠ a̠sibh rologi d̠i̠yar na̠ akparame̠ni̠ na̠ a̠guri d̠a̠ eko bho̠. Na̠ awo̠l na̠ a̠ten e̠nu̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ a̠lukpesi e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠a̠ otuta̠zib̠a̠,  
\v 20 esi wa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠ia̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠yar bho̠. I̠se̠n i̠na na̠ a̠ten we̠mu̠ rokur kid̠ud̠ul, d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ta̠ Ame̠lkize̠de̠k. 
\c 7  
\s1 Ame̠lkize̠de̠k We̠mu̠ Okur Bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Ame̠lkize̠de̠k onon aro̠ ma̠ o̠li̠le̠ma Asale̠m na̠ okur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Wagi̠manyu̠ A̠pu bho̠. I̠na a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ Ebraham a̠tutumeni, ma̠ igiel bho̠ Ebraham ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ aru̠lala e̠ma bho̠ sa̠ na̠ a̠mula̠ na̠ a̠yel bho̠,  
\v 2 sa̠ Ebraham a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ odi a̠bin d̠a̠ atu̠gi̠ a̠d̠iobh d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠bhin bho̠. O̠pu̠r ezin a̠d̠ien ta̠ Ame̠lkizede̠k bha̠ “o̠li̠le̠ma e̠b̠ab̠ala”, opa̠n ezin sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ “o̠li̠le̠ma ekima̠.”  
\v 3 I̠na o̠wede̠ bo̠ onweni bo̠, o̠la-imitia̠n ibom ro̠we̠de̠ na̠ ronweni id̠ud̠ul bo̠, i̠na na̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel eru a̠ghud̠um na̠ obhel oyel nyen, ya̠a̠ u̠le̠m i̠na o̠gu̠b̠e̠ni̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ okur tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul.  
\v 4 Ikpone ma̠ ed̠ighom e̠mi̠ alu̠bu̠gh d̠o̠yo̠; aga̠i Ebraham wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ obom o̠we̠de̠ id̠ud̠ul bho̠ eka̠, a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ odi a̠bin d̠a̠ atu̠gi̠ a̠d̠iobh d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ilei abar ipu d̠a̠ ologi i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠bhin bho̠.  
\v 5 Oloko bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠limon anwi̠i̠ny imitia̠n ta̠ A̠livai̠ ya̠ id̠igh rokur bho̠, ma̠ obhin odi a̠bin d̠a̠ atu̠gi̠ a̠d̠iobh d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ a̠nwunom bho̠. O̠ku̠a na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, awa na̠ ebhin d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun Izre̠l agu̠o̠ awa, ya̠ i̠ro̠ ani̠ ma̠ imitia̠n ta̠ Ebraham bho̠.  
\v 6 Ame̠lkize̠de̠k na̠ omite̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠la ta̠ A̠livai̠, ku̠ku̠m eka̠ i̠na a̠bhin odi a̠bin d̠a̠ atu̠gi̠ a̠d̠iobh bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ Ebraham a̠tutumeni i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ rogua̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠ro̠ inigha̠ bho̠.  
\v 7 Ologhom ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu bho̠ na̠ a̠tutumeni gha̠n o̠ni̠ wa̠ aki̠r a̠pu i̠na bho̠, aku̠anan bo̠no̠bo̠.  
\v 8 D̠a̠ e̠kal wa̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ rokur bho̠, bha̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ta̠ emugughu na̠ ebhin odi a̠bin d̠a̠ atu̠gi̠ a̠d̠iobh bho̠; ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ opa̠n e̠kal, bha̠ i̠na wa̠ u̠gba umutiom ma̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠ na̠ a̠bhin.  
\v 9 D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gba bha̠, aga̠i A̠levai̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin odi a̠bin d̠a̠ atu̠gi̠ a̠d̠iobh bho̠ eka̠, awo̠l d̠a̠ Ebraham akpe̠ ghan odi a̠bin d̠a̠ atu̠gi̠ a̠d̠iobh bho̠,  
\v 10 ezin bho̠ A̠livai̠ od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ eghun obom o̠we̠de̠ id̠ud̠ul d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ igiel bho̠ Ame̠lkize̠de̠k ate̠i̠ Ebraham bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s agu̠ban Ame̠lkize̠de̠k 
\p  
\v 11 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, a̠nwunom ta̠ erue e̠wo̠l d̠a̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ta̠ rokur ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ imitia̠n ta̠ A̠livai̠ bho̠ e̠te̠i̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠nye̠ i̠gbo̠ d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ imite bho̠, ka̠ ezin wa̠ opa̠n okur ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ta̠ Ame̠lkize̠de̠k ta̠ a̠mite a̠ru bho̠, ola̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ ita̠ Ero̠n bho̠, ka̠ ere?  
\v 12 Ezin bho̠, igiel a̠dila̠de okur bho̠ a̠nwegia̠n, bha̠ oloko bho̠ eka̠ ta̠ awegia̠n nyen.  
\v 13 O̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ o̠gba ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ ogboloma̠ bho̠, a̠mite d̠a̠ opa̠n ebhugh. Ebhugh d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ emutiom o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ aro̠ ato̠to̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠a̠ enwen bho̠.  
\v 14 O̠mar ologhom ma̠a̠, Wa̠nwuna̠ wa̠ na̠ o̠gba ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ ogboloma̠ bho̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ eghun ta̠ A̠zuda̠, sa̠ A̠mozizi na̠ osen d̠o̠ ma̠ eghun obha̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de okur.  
\v 15 Ta̠ o̠mar o̠mu̠gho̠nyan abar wa̠ i̠yar u̠gba bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ opa̠n okur ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ta̠ Ame̠lkize̠de̠k na̠ a̠mite bho̠,  
\v 16 i̠na wa̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de okur, ola̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ oloko e̠ma-ra̠nwunom o̠ri̠lo̠me̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ ubhin d̠a̠ a̠limon a̠ghud̠um wa̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ bho̠.  
\v 17 U̠gba d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ omutiom ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Anwa ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ okur tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul, ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ta̠ Ame̠lkize̠de̠k.” 
\p  
\v 18 Na̠ ogbogion ugba̠iny oloko bho̠, ezin bho̠ odudugha̠n na̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠ abar.  
\v 19 Ezin bho̠, abar ola̠ oloko bho̠ a̠rue ma̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ bo̠, ya̠a̠ na̠ omutiom eb̠em ologi ola̠ a̠bhon a̠pu, ola̠ ta̠ o̠wo̠l o̠te̠i̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 20 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠ bha̠, i̠na na̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ okur ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ od̠ia̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠zo̠ a̠gboloma̠, ya̠a̠ ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠zo̠ o̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom iyed̠i ma̠ rokur.  
\v 21 Ya̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠d̠ia̠n i̠zo̠ alo̠gh i̠na ma̠ okur agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠sibhigha̠ sa̠ i̠na ko onwe d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠. Anwa ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ okur tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul.” 
\pi1  
\v 22 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ten o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ amara ma̠ eni na̠ a̠leriom ma̠a̠ omom i̠zo̠ bho̠ a̠bhon a̠pu.  
\v 23 Opa̠n a̠nwegia̠n od̠i, ezin bho̠, a̠d̠izo rokur iyed̠i imugughu d̠a̠ egum sa̠ i̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de bho̠ egir e̠gi̠o̠m d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠.  
\v 24 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul bho̠, bha̠ ogir okur d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ okunugiom d̠o̠.  
\v 25 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rue na̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠wo̠l d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠. Ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rugh a̠ghud̠um o̠mara eni onigha̠ awa d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ kigiel kigiel.  
\v 26 O̠ku̠a bha̠ i̠na we̠mu̠ okur ola̠ igielake̠ na̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala, o̠ni̠ abar o̠li̠o̠m o̠to̠ na̠ i̠karabh o̠to̠. Uguri i̠na osigimeni ma̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh, sa̠ ub̠eton i̠na u̠gi̠o̠m anyu̠ upeleni ma̠ re̠nai̠ny bho̠.  
\v 27 I̠na bo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur iyed̠i. A̠dila̠de okur d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ opuru d̠o̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠kpe̠gi̠ ralu̠kpe̠ ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠d̠a̠ma̠, ya̠ od̠ia̠ obhin otenemeni i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ akpe̠gi̠ ma̠ iya̠ otenemeni i̠karabh a̠nwunom bho̠. I̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ a̠bhin akpe̠ ma̠ i̠karabh d̠awa ma̠ onin ogbudon sa̠ a̠munia̠n i̠se̠.  
\v 28 Ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur ya̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ alo̠gi̠ bho̠ idudugha̠n d̠a̠ re̠kal, ya̠a̠ i̠zo̠ wa̠ a̠ru ma̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠ aso̠n i̠na O̠nyi̠ bho̠, wa̠ na̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ oguri tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul bho̠. 
\c 8  
\p  
\v 1 Onon e̠mu̠ abar wa̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠gba bho̠. I̠yar unwuna̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ okur ola̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ a̠lukpesi ta̠ Wa̠lei Abar A̠pu bho̠ d̠a̠ renai̠ny.  
\v 2 I̠na ob̠a̠ra̠motu e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠a̠ a̠lukpesi e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠ga̠i otu-akpu̠ru̠ wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gim bho̠, wa̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ogim d̠o̠ bho̠.  
\v 3 We̠mu̠ okur we̠mu̠ okur ola̠ u̠so̠n na̠ a̠bhin gha̠n i̠di̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ na̠ i̠nam i̠ko̠l na̠ ako̠l i̠ko̠l. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, sa̠ a̠bhon we̠mu̠ okur onon onwuna̠ ani̠ abar ola̠ obhin o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠.  
\v 4 Aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ i̠na od̠i d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom nab̠o̠, i̠na ka̠ id̠igh d̠o̠ na̠ od̠igh okur, ezin bho̠ rokur ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m oloko bho̠ na̠ ebhin i̠di̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ na̠ e̠kpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ od̠i.  
\v 5 I̠ko̠l d̠awa od̠i ka̠ o̠ru̠ran abar ola̠ na̠ egir na̠ e̠gu̠b̠e̠ni̠ ma̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar ote̠nai̠ny. Obha̠ ezin bho̠ u̠kparame̠ni̠ ukikiom A̠mozizi ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ ra̠ ogim otu-akpu̠ru̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Mare̠ ma̠ a̠kpon a̠gir kabar kabar agu̠b̠e̠ni̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ uleriom anwa d̠a̠ igu bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n, na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s opa̠n a̠d̠ien ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar okur ya̠ ilei abar ipu ma̠ ita̠ awa. Od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ rogua̠n d̠a̠ i̠zo̠ wa̠ i̠na na̠ amara eni bho̠, ibhon ipu ma̠ ita̠ oloko bho̠.  
\v 7 I̠se̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ api̠an d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r i̠zo̠ bho̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ na̠b̠o̠, ezin ola̠ o̠tu̠n omutiom wa̠leghemeni i̠wal bho̠ ka̠ i̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 8 Agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ abi̠gh ma̠ awa na̠ egir na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “I̠nagha! Ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ na̠ eru ma̠ igiel ami̠ ta̠ a̠mutiom omom i̠zo̠ a̠d̠ia̠n na̠ a̠nwunom Izre̠l na̠ a̠nwunom A̠zuda̠. 
\q2  
\v 9 Obha̠ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠zo̠ wa̠ ami̠ id̠ia̠n na̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ id̠ud̠ul d̠awa bho̠, ma̠ igiel bho̠ ami̠ isibh awa d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ irileghom imutiom d̠a̠ Izipt bho̠. Igiel obha̠, awa i̠b̠agh aru̠mu̠ e̠we̠le̠man obhin d̠a̠ igielake̠ okoko i̠zo̠ bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ ighel awa.” 
\p  
\v 10 Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Onon i̠zo̠ wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠n na̠ a̠nwunom Izre̠l ma̠a̠, 
\q2 ‘D̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠, ami̠ ta̠ alo̠gi̠ ma̠ roloko d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa, age̠ d̠a̠ rekpo ologi d̠awa. Ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ da̠wa, sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠ami̠.’ 
\q2  
\v 11 o̠ni̠ awa ola̠ ta̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, bo̠d̠o̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ opa̠n o̠nyi̠ eghun ma̠a̠, ‘Loghome ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠,’ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, ezin bho̠ eb̠la̠ awa ta̠ eloghom ami̠, i̠gbara na̠ ikei. 
\q2  
\v 12 Ami̠ ta̠ a̠kpon i̠karabh d̠awa asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien, sa̠ ami̠ ko o̠ru̠ru̠an mu ma̠ i̠karabh od̠ighi i̠di̠ar d̠awa.” 
\p  
\v 13 Agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ agba ma̠a̠ omom i̠zo̠ onon a̠bhon a̠pu bho̠, bha̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ o̠pu̠r bho̠ ma̠ ugba̠iny. Ologhom ma̠a̠, abar ola̠ na̠ a̠ten ugba̠iny sa̠ ko orue mu orughom ma̠a̠, na̠ a̠tua̠n ebhi abar bho̠ ma̠ oghur oten. 
\c 9  
\ms1 I̠ko̠l d̠a̠ Otu-akpu̠ru̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ a̠de onon 
\p  
\v 1 O̠pu̠r i̠zo̠ bho̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ na̠ a̠lukpesi ola̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ko̠l i̠ko̠l.  
\v 2 Otu-akpu̠ru̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ ugim. O̠pu̠r e̠kpe̠ bho̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠lukpesi E̠tu̠tu̠, esi ola̠ uguri ma̠ o̠lo̠ ato̠di̠ na̠ akpata ola̠ u̠gbamagi̠ ikpokpogh abre̠di̠.  
\v 3 D̠a̠ aman wa̠leghemeni i̠wal ukpe wa̠ ubhin usobhom A̠lukpesi E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, bha̠ opa̠n e̠kpe̠ od̠i ma̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠a̠ Obom A̠lukpesi E̠tu̠tu̠,  
\v 4 esi bho̠ enwen i̠tani̠ ed̠u-e̠nu̠nu̠ ola̠ ubhin a̠gol u̠le̠m, na̠ obom igba̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ola̠ ubhin a̠gol ukelema̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ozu sa̠ ud̠ighom okpa̠ko ola̠ ubhin a̠gol u̠le̠m od̠i bho̠. U̠b̠aram na̠ okpeti ta̠ Ero̠n wa̠ na̠ aghu̠r bho̠, na̠ ipopola̠ ro̠gbi̠o̠ma ya̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ od̠ighom d̠a̠ ologi obom igba̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠,  
\v 5 sa̠ Itileduom isosorogia̠n od̠i d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠ na̠ eghughuom a̠lukpesi wa̠ na̠ okpon i̠karabh na̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien bho̠. Ya̠a̠ i̠yar ko orue d̠o̠ o̠gba ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n o̠si̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n.  
\v 6 Igiel na̠ o̠mar o̠to̠to̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠ oguri ma̠ o̠ko̠no̠n, sa̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ e̠kpe̠ wa̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ bho̠ na̠ egir gha̠n ogir ya̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠.  
\v 7 Ya̠a̠, We̠mu̠ Okur bho̠ ku̠ku̠m na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ e̠kpe̠ wa̠ d̠a̠ ologi bho̠. I̠na na̠ a̠d̠igh gha̠n i̠se̠ ma̠ onin igiel d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ ala, sa̠ na̠ o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠b̠aram na̠ asi̠ ya̠ obhin o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠ otenemeni ozu d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ i̠karabh ya̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ologhoma̠n d̠o̠ sa̠ igir.  
\v 8 Ob̠eb̠i E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠bhin i̠nye̠ na̠ a̠leriom ma̠a̠, ta̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ omutiom agu̠o̠ o̠wo̠l od̠igh d̠a̠ Obom A̠lukpesi E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ebula̠ agu̠o̠ o̠pu̠r e̠kpe̠ Otu-akpu̠ru̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ od̠id̠ia̠ bho̠.  
\v 9 Onon elegh ola̠ na̠ a̠leriom agu̠o̠ i̠di̠ar ta̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m onon, ma̠ i̠di̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ na̠ ralu̠kpe̠ ya̠ na̠ o̠kpe̠ na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ irue d̠o̠ e̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi o̠ni̠ i̠ko̠l bho̠ a̠guri d̠a̠ igielake̠.  
\v 10 Ri̠to̠to̠gi̠ i̠ye̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ od̠e na̠ o̠d̠a ku̠ku̠m na̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere agu̠o̠ obhin o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ a̠ruzu d̠i̠yar. I̠ye̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ipulupul ozu ya̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ka̠ e̠te̠i̠ obhel wa̠ ta̠ omutiom imom i̠di̠ar onwe awa bho̠.  
\v 11 Ya̠a̠, Akrai̠st a̠ru ma̠ agu̠o̠ Obom Okur ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar, sa̠ i̠ye̠ ologhom od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠. I̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh nyen d̠a̠ otu-akpu̠ru̠ ola̠ abu̠gh a̠pu sa̠ a̠bhon a̠pu, ola̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ogim (olo), ola̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ u̠le̠m ani̠ d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom onon.  
\v 12 Igiel bho̠ Akrai̠st agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ A̠lukpesi Obom E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠ obhel sa̠ opa̠n igiel ko o̠ro̠ mu̠ bho̠, i̠na na̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ asi̠ iwel na̠ anwi̠ny ranama, ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠bhin asi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ ata̠ i̠yar asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh, ma̠ i̠yar o̠te̠i̠ itenemeni ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠.  
\v 13 Agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eru ra̠ o̠ko̠l i̠ko̠l o̠b̠ab̠ala d̠o̠, sa̠ na̠ ozughoghom asi̠ rekpe na̠ ilobhiri anama na̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ awa d̠a̠ ozu bho̠,  
\v 14 sa̠ asi̠ ta̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠gir a̠peleni ma̠ o̠ku̠a. Ezin bho̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ i̠karabh o̠to̠, ola̠ a̠bhin ozu d̠o̠yo̠ akpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ e̠mu̠gh ola̠ ta̠ aro̠ kid̠ud̠ul a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ma̠ o̠bab̠alame̠ni̠ i̠walama ologi o̠si̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh od̠ighi i̠di̠ar, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠yar ogir ogir onigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠.  
\v 15 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠na a̠ten o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ amara ma̠ enie d̠a̠ omom i̠zo̠ onon wa̠ a̠bhon a̠pu (ma̠ ugbany) bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ obhelegi bho̠ ed̠e ma̠ ad̠i̠a e̠no̠gho̠man kid̠ud̠ul ya̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n bho̠. Ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠mugh a̠tenemeni awa d̠a̠ i̠karabh ya̠ awa igir d̠a̠ ekpukpu i̠zo̠ wa̠ a̠d̠ia̠ aro̠ bho̠.  
\v 16 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ a̠gurigia̠n igurugia̠n bha̠, na̠ ob̠a̠ra̠ gha̠n ka̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠mugh kisa̠ na̠ okpon na̠ o̠to̠to̠gi̠.  
\v 17 Ezin bho̠ igurugia̠n bho̠ id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠gurigia̠n bho̠ od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um. Igiel o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠mugh kisa̠ na̠ okpon (agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠gurugia̠n bho̠) na̠ o̠to̠to̠gi̠.  
\v 18 Obha̠ ezin bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠, d̠a̠ ugba̠ny i̠zo̠ bho̠ eka̠, ubhin asi̠ u̠kpo̠ ma̠ e̠la.  
\v 19 A̠mozizi agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ roloko ya̠ i̠kpe̠ awa ma̠ okoko bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na agu̠a ma̠ asi̠ olobhiri anama na̠ ekpe d̠a̠ amu̠m, sa̠ ato̠ri̠ ma̠ afu̠lafu̠ ododo na̠ i̠mu̠n ahi̠so̠p a̠bhin asi̠saragi̠o̠m obhurugho a̠d̠ire bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠a̠, “I̠nye̠n asi̠ ya̠ ubhin u̠kpo̠ ma̠ e̠la d̠a̠ i̠zo̠ wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠d̠ia̠n na̠ i̠nyin bho̠.  
\v 21 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ A̠mozizi asi̠saragi̠o̠m otu-akpu̠ru̠ bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ rokpa̠ko i̠ko̠lo̠gi̠ bho̠ ma̠ asi̠ bho̠.  
\v 22 D̠a̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ Oloko bho̠, aro̠ ka̠ na̠ obhin asi̠ na̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ kabar kabar, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ okpon i̠karabh o̠si̠ghe̠ a̠d̠ien ko omite d̠o̠, a̠ten ka̠ uzu ma̠ asi̠.  
\v 23 Obha̠ a̠d̠ighi kisa̠ na̠ obhin i̠to̠to̠gi̠ i̠ye̠ na̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ta d̠a̠ ote̠nany bho̠. Ya̠a̠ na̠ obhin i̠di̠ar i̠ko̠l ya̠ ibhon ipu ma̠ i̠ye̠ na̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ o̠te̠nany na̠ agu̠o̠.  
\v 24 Ezin bho̠, Akrai̠st na̠ o̠gi̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ra̠lukpesi e̠b̠ab̠ala ya̠ a̠nwunom i̠le̠m ya̠ i̠gu̠b̠a̠n kuma̠ aga̠i a̠yi bho̠, ya̠a̠, i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ aga̠i o̠yo̠. I̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ote̠nany na̠ agu̠o̠, d̠a̠ esi bho̠ od̠i na̠ amara ma̠ enie na̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.  
\v 25 I̠na na̠ o̠gi̠ d̠o̠ nyen d̠a̠ A̠lukpesi E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠ obhin ozu d̠o̠yo̠ o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠izo igiel, agu̠o̠ Obokur A̠zu na̠ a̠d̠igh gha̠n d̠a̠ ologi na̠ a̠bhin asi̠ ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ o̠yo̠ na̠ ako̠lo̠gi̠ kala kala bho̠.  
\v 26 Aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ i̠na a̠bhin ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ako̠l i̠ko̠l kala kala nab̠o̠, sa̠ i̠na ka̠ i̠bi̠gh ali̠gam a̠luzu ma̠ a̠d̠izo igiel ka̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠. Ya̠a̠, i̠se̠n ekunuguma̠ ramu̠m bho̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ onin igiel amado̠n, ma̠ obhin o̠kpe̠ a̠lu̠kpe̠ okunugiom a̠limon i̠karabh.  
\v 27 Ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠mugh onin igiel, sa̠ ka̠ a̠ten i̠se̠ sa̠ ta̠ osobh ase̠ ogboloma̠ i̠na.  
\v 28 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ Akrai̠st a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ onin igiel amado̠n, ma̠ obhin o̠kpe̠ a̠lu̠kpe̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ i̠karabh d̠a̠ a̠ruzu a̠d̠izo ogbo. Ya̠a̠, obhel i̠na ta̠ a̠mite a̠ru ma̠ oleghemeni i̠wal igiel bho̠, i̠na ko oru d̠o̠ ma̠ ra̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ i̠karabh. I̠na ta̠ atu̠n ra̠ otenemeni ogbo ya̠ na̠ ebhin d̠a̠ ebhiroma̠ na̠ egon i̠na bho̠ a̠ru. 
\c 10  
\s1 Alu̠kpe̠ wa̠ Akrai̠st akpe̠ amado̠n bho̠ (Alu̠kpe̠ wa̠ Akrai̠st akpe̠ ma̠ onin igiel sa̠ ko o̠kpe̠ mu̠ bho̠) 
\p  
\v 1 Ta̠ obhin Oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi o̠tu̠o̠m okokogh ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ eru bho̠. Okokogh onon ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠, ezin bho̠, ko o̠wo̠l d̠o̠ d̠a̠ onin a̠d̠ien ralu̠kpe̠ ya̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠kpe̠ o̠kpe̠ kala kala bho̠ sa̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eru ra̠ o̠ko̠l o̠yo̠ bho̠ ta̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala.  
\v 2 I̠se̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eru ra̠ o̠ko̠l o̠yo̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala nab̠o̠, sa̠ awa ka̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an mu ma̠a̠ awa e̠pi̠o̠gho̠m (na̠ egir i̠karabh), sa̠ ezin ola̠ odin o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠ ka̠ i̠ro̠ mu̠.  
\v 3 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ ralu̠kpe̠ i̠ye̠ na̠ enumeta̠n awa ma̠ i̠karabh d̠awa kala kala.  
\v 4 Ezin bho̠, asi̠ ilobhiri anama na̠ rekpe i̠si̠ghe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh.  
\v 5 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, igiel bho̠ Akrai̠st na̠ ra̠ oru d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Anwa na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠ko̠lo̠gi̠ na̠ ralu̠kpe̠, ya̠a̠ ozu d̠ami̠ wa̠ anwa na̠ atu̠ghu̠man a̠guri bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 6 O̠bhu̠gi̠ ikpo i̠nam alu̠kpe̠ ya̠ obhin o̠si̠ghe̠ i̠karabh d̠o̠ na̠ ebhonomeni ma̠ ologi d̠oyom.  
\v 7 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “E A̠zib̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠ru ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ma̠ ami̠ igir d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠oyom.”  
\v 8 I̠na na̠ a̠d̠ia̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠ko̠lo̠gi̠ na̠ ralu̠kpe̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ikpo i̠nam alu̠kpe̠ apu̠gi̠ ya̠ na̠ odin i̠karabh na̠ o̠kpe̠, d̠a̠ eb̠ula̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠to̠to̠gi̠ Oloko wa̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠ eka̠.  
\v 9 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n ogir agu̠o̠ anwa i̠to̠ bho̠.” Sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gbogion eb̠la̠ igba̠iny i̠ko̠lo̠gi̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin alu̠kpe̠ ta̠ Akra̠ist wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ omom bho̠ a̠dinom.  
\v 10 Ebula̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st a̠gir agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ato̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠yar u̠wo̠l d̠a̠ onin obhel alu̠kpe̠ wa̠ i̠na a̠bhin ozu d̠o̠yo̠ akpe̠ bho̠, uten a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala.  
\v 11 Ad̠u̠a ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ a̠ten a̠d̠a̠ma̠, kokur kokur na̠ amara na̠ a̠bhin onin a̠d̠ien alu̠kpe̠ na̠ ako̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠ko̠l d̠a̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠, ku̠ku̠m eka̠ ri̠ko̠l i̠ye̠ irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ i̠karabh.  
\v 12 Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ Akrai̠st a̠bhin ozu d̠o̠yo̠ akpe̠ ma̠ onin obhel alu̠kpe̠ ata ma̠ i̠karabh awe̠le̠ bho̠, ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ wa̠ ta̠ aro̠ tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 13 Ob̠eton d̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ i̠na od̠i na̠ a̠gon igiel ta̠ otenemeni ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ okpokpolom o̠gbam a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 14 Ezin bho̠, ta̠ o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ alu̠kpe̠ wa̠ i̠na akpe̠ ma̠ onin obhel bho̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aso̠n bho̠ tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul.  
\v 15 E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ (E̠mu̠gh E̠b̠ab̠ala, Ob̠eb̠i E̠mu̠gh) bho̠ agba nyen a̠nigha̠ i̠yar agu̠o̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n i̠ro̠ ma̠ ya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠ ma̠a̠:  
\v 16 “Igiel ta̠ ate̠i̠ obhel bho̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠n awa ma̠ i̠zo̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ age̠ ma̠ roloko d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ rekpo ologi d̠awa na̠ d̠a̠ amu̠gho̠nyan (i̠walama ologi) d̠awa.  
\v 17 Sa̠ ami̠ ko o̠ru̠ru̠an mu̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠karabh d̠awa na̠ ado̠l i̠te̠i̠ d̠awa.”  
\v 18 Igiel A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠kpon i̠karabh o̠ni̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien, ezin ola̠ odin o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠ ya̠ o̠ta i̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠ bo̠.  
\v 19 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ onin ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠, awo̠l d̠a̠ asi̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s sa̠ i̠yar unwuna̠ ma̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi od̠igh d̠a̠ Obom A̠lukpesi E̠tu̠tu̠ (E̠b̠ab̠ala) bho̠,  
\v 20 wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ omom eten a̠ghud̠um ola̠ ubhin ozu d̠o̠yo̠ uguron unigha̠ i̠yar.  
\v 21 I̠yar onwuna̠ ma̠ obom okur ola̠ na̠ a̠kponom Otuta̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 22 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, id̠ighi obhin rologi e̠b̠ab̠ala na̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi id̠umom d̠i̠yar oru d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Id̠ighi oguri ma̠ rologi d̠i̠yar d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala, o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ i̠karabh i̠walama, obhin amu̠m otitol a̠ruzu d̠i̠yar o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠.  
\v 23 Id̠ighi osibh o̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ eb̠em ologi wa̠ i̠yar na̠ oma̠ra̠ bho̠, ezin bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ i̠yar bho̠ ola̠ obhin ob̠em ologi.  
\v 24 Odi akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi ta̠ odi ma̠ ogir ib̠eb̠i d̠a̠ etula̠n.  
\v 25 I̠yar o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ osor gha̠n ezue od̠igh onin, ma̠ agu̠o̠ idi ogbo na̠ egir bho̠, ya̠a̠ odi akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi ta̠ odi, okunukun i̠se̠n wa̠ eruoma̠ d̠o̠yo̠ (ta̠ Akrai̠st) na̠ a̠tua̠n bho̠.  
\v 26 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠yar o̠ro̠ ma̠ ogir ogir i̠karabh i̠se̠n i̠yar na̠ o̠mar ologhom ya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠, sa̠ opa̠n alu̠kpe̠ ola̠ ta̠ orue obhin o̠kpe̠ otenemeni i̠yar d̠a̠ i̠karabh ko o̠ro̠ mu̠.  
\v 27 Abar wa̠ od̠i bho̠ bha̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ a̠rugugu egon osobh ase̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ obom e̠ba anya wa̠ ta̠ anu̠o̠me̠ni̠ (a̠kunugi) awa bho̠.  
\v 28 Ezin bho̠ u̠to̠ ma̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ a̠sor oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi sa̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom imite i̠gba ma̠ onyob̠a̠, bha̠ ta̠ ogigh o̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 29 O̠ku̠a ka̠a̠, inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠ agu̠o̠ i̠zagba wa̠ ta̠ o̠gu̠r ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekpon O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ e̠do̠ti̠me̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ na̠ e̠pi̠o̠gho̠m i̠zo̠ asi̠ wa̠ ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ awa bho̠, sa̠ na̠ efugh i̠basi̠ ma̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ka̠ ta̠ aro̠ (abu̠gh a̠lei) eka̠?  
\v 30 I̠yar ologhom ma̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠e awa ma̠ olo. Ami̠ ta̠ akpe̠ awa.” 
\p I̠na agba nyen ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “WA̠NWUNA̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠.” 
\p  
\v 31 Ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ abar a̠rugugu ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ omel od̠igh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠limon wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠.  
\v 32 I̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r igiel wa̠ inyin ud̠ia̠ uloghom Akrai̠st bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin uwia̠n une ma̠ a̠ma̠ne d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ali̠gam a̠ruzu (egbika̠).  
\v 33 A̠mite ma̠ ola̠ urogi gha̠n inyin sa̠ ugbikimeni inyin d̠a̠ etire, ipa̠n igiel sa̠ inyin ud̠igh na̠ ipa̠n ogbo u̠bi̠gh ani̠ ma̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ awa bho̠.  
\v 34 Inyin o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ ma̠ (okpon igbirigbir) ogbo ikoli, sa̠ igiel bho̠ ughumi ma̠ i̠di̠ar d̠inyin ubhinogh bho̠, sa̠ inyin ubhin d̠a̠ ibo na̠ a̠ma̠ne u̠da ubhin, ezin bho̠, inyin ologhom ma̠a̠ inyin onwuna̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ibhon ipu ma̠ i̠ye̠ ya̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul.  
\v 35 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ko orobh alu̠kpo̠ ologi wa̠ inyin unwuna̠ bho̠, ezin bho̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ibom asu̠wo̠ a̠ruom inyin.  
\v 36 Akpe̠ inyin one a̠ma̠ne, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin orue ogir agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ato̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠nyin ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n bho̠.  
\v 37 Ezin bho̠, A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Ekud̠i obhel ku̠ku̠m a̠sugho, sa̠ i̠na wa̠ ta̠ a̠ru bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru. I̠na ko orobh d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel.” 
\p  
\v 38 Sa̠, 
\q1 “A̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i na̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala bho̠ ta̠ ed̠um ebula̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa. Ya̠a̠, ologi d̠ami̠ ko obhon d̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ awa ola̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ d̠a̠ aman.” 
\p  
\v 39 I̠yar bo̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ emula̠ d̠a̠ aman sa̠ a̠d̠ugh a̠bhin (sa̠ imugh ibhe) bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠yar od̠i d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ (ta̠) a̠tenemeni awa bho̠. 
\c 11  
\s1 Ologi Ima̠ra̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Ologi ima̠ra̠ bha̠ abar ola̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar eb̠em ologi na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠yar ko orue d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh.  
\v 2 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ na̠ ronweni d̠i̠yar igied̠i i̠te̠i̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 3 Na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ i̠yar u̠mu̠gho̠nyan ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ale̠m e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ a̠soroni. Sa̠ a̠mite ma̠ ola̠ ubhin i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠yar ko orue d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh bho̠ u̠le̠m i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠bi̠gh bho̠.  
\v 4 Ebe̠l a̠bhin d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ akpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ ola̠ a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠ken. Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ada i̠na a̠bhin agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ igielake̠. I̠di̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ Ebe̠l ed̠igh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ologi, sa̠ eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠mugh bho̠ eka̠, bha̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠yo̠ od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ agba ma̠ abar na̠ a̠gboloma̠ i̠na.  
\v 5 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ I̠no̠k omugh d̠o̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhuneni i̠na d̠a̠ o̠te̠nany, obha̠ ezin bho̠ a̠nwunom orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. I̠no̠k a̠rugh a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ologi.  
\v 6 O̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠rugh a̠ma̠rugh ya̠ ta̠ ed̠igh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ologi bo̠, a̠ten ka̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠. O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ ebhir oru d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠loghoma̠n ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ od̠i, sa̠ na̠ akpe̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠gh ologhom o̠yo̠ bho̠.  
\v 7 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ A̠noa̠ anagha ma̠ o̠kparakpar a̠kikiom ola̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠d̠iar ya̠ i̠na ta̠ od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ abi̠gh. I̠na anagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na ale̠m obom oghugh abadi̠ ola̠ ta̠ obhin otenemeni ma̠ eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ i̠na. Agbo̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠kunugi ma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ A̠noa̠ ra̠ a̠ten o̠ni̠ (a̠d̠e ma̠ ad̠i̠a) e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠a̠ ebula̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 8 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ Ebraham anagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ igiel bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhelegi i̠na ma̠ o̠d̠u̠a o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ a̠de wa̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ o̠yo̠ bho̠. Ebraham ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ebhugh d̠o̠yo̠ agi̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ i̠na ologhom d̠o̠.  
\v 9 I̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ a̠rugh agu̠o̠ isuloma̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ i̠na bho̠. I̠na a̠rugh d̠a̠ a̠rutu akpu̠ru̠, onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ Azi̠ki̠ na̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠ irugh d̠a̠ a̠rutu akpu̠ru̠ nyen, sa̠ i̠te̠i̠ ani̠ ma̠ onin ogua̠n bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 10 Ebraham a̠gir o̠ku̠a, ezin bho̠ i̠na aro̠ a̠gon e̠ma wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠gbonogi a̠lo a̠guri bho̠, wa̠ ta̠ aro̠ tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul bho̠.  
\v 11 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ nyen sa̠ Ebraham a̠ten o̠we̠de̠ d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ A̠sera na̠ akpo̠ a̠pu ma̠ omumor o̠nyi̠ sa̠ i̠na eka̠ na̠ akpo̠. I̠na a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠sibh ogua̠n d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 12 O̠ku̠a bha̠ eb̠la̠ ekpom ebhugh awo̠l a̠mite d̠a̠ onin o̠ni̠ onon wa̠ aro̠ ka̠ na̠ a̠ten e̠mar bho̠. Ebhugh ola̠ ibom a̠b̠utu (a̠d̠izo) a̠nwunom od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠ni̠nany d̠a̠ ote̠nany na̠ i̠si̠sar d̠a̠ esoroma̠ abadi̠, ma̠ iya̠ o̠nu̠ o̠wal o̠to̠.  
\v 13 Eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n emugughu ya̠a̠ enwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠. Awa i̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠, ya̠a̠ awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ esi egbeny e̠bi̠gh, sa̠ awa i̠da ibhin. Awa ima̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ awa risuloma̠ ya̠ ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a ma̠ esi eten esi ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠de onon.  
\v 14 A̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ku̠a, ibhin ma̠a̠ awa na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh ebhugh ola̠ awa ta̠ obhelegi ma̠ ola̠ awa.  
\v 15 Aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ghan igboloma̠ ma̠ ebhugh wa̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a iru bho̠ nab̠o̠, obhel ka̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ ola̠ awa ka̠ imula̠.  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, ibhir awa ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ abar ola̠ a̠d̠igh asu̠wo̠ a̠pu ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nany. Obha̠ ezin bho̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l ma̠ awa ma̠ obhelegi o̠yo̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠we̠de̠ d̠awa. I̠na a̠lo nyen e̠ma a̠guri a̠sisa̠n awa.  
\v 17 Ugua̠n unigha̠ ma̠ Ebraham ma̠a̠ ta̠ o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ Azi̠ki̠ o̠nyi̠ i̠mara ilologia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ omuzoghod̠iom i̠di̠ar i̠ye̠. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n obhin Azi̠ki̠ o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠,  
\v 18 ma̠ eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Azi̠ki̠ o̠nyi̠ wa̠ anwi̠ny i̠sabh ikpele (anwi̠ny o̠gu̠man) d̠oyom ta̠ e̠wo̠l emite bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 19 Ebraham aru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠, ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ Azi̠ki̠ a̠mugh eka̠, ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠mulumeni i̠na a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um. Agu̠o̠ o̠gba bha̠, umulumeni ma̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ebraham d̠a̠ omugh oruom i̠na.  
\v 20 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ Azi̠ki̠ a̠du ma̠ o̠gho̠r ib̠eb̠i ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ a̠nigha̠ (a̠tutumeni) ma̠ anwi̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠ na̠ I̠so̠.  
\v 21 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠ a̠du ma̠ o̠gho̠r ib̠eb̠i a̠nigha̠ (a̠tutumeni) ma̠ anwi̠ny ta̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ ma̠ odi odi i̠se̠, ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ten okei-o̠ni̠ a̠tua̠n omugh bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ab̠e̠d̠i̠an d̠a̠ okpeti d̠o̠yo̠ a̠zuma̠n d̠a̠ a̠siseiny.  
\v 22 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwi̠ny Izre̠l ma̠ awa ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ Izipt, ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ru ra̠ omugh bho̠, sa̠ a̠ruom nyen agu̠o̠ awa ta̠ egir egboloma̠ ma̠ i̠kpo̠kpo̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 23 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ ta̠ A̠mozizi i̠wo̠gi̠ i̠na ma̠ obhel ola̠ a̠lei i̠sar uwetire ma̠ igiel bho̠ u̠mar i̠na bho̠. Ezin bho̠, awa i̠bi̠gh a̠libhon o̠nyi̠ bho̠ sa̠ ighil d̠o̠ ma̠ oloko wa̠ o̠li̠le̠ma alo̠gh bho̠.  
\v 24 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ A̠mozizi oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ obhelegi i̠na ma̠ i̠na o̠nyi̠ o̠nyani̠ ta̠ Afe̠ro.  
\v 25 I̠na a̠bhin a̠bin wa̠ od̠igh na̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ogbika̠ bho̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ od̠e e̠nu̠m i̠karabh ya̠ na̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ ekud̠i obhel ku̠ku̠m bho̠.  
\v 26 A̠mozizi a̠loghom ma̠a̠, i̠na ma̠ ogbika̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ asu̠wo̠ ya̠ ilei abar a̠pu ma̠ e̠no̠gho̠man Izipt bho̠.  
\v 27 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ A̠mozizi ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ Izipt sa̠ i̠na oghil d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠gam ta̠ o̠li̠le̠ma. I̠na a̠ne, aro̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwunom o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien bho̠.  
\v 28 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ A̠mozizi a̠koko ma̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠, na̠ ozu asi̠ b̠o̠ka̠ a̠d̠ugh wa̠ na̠ aze̠ ma̠ i̠kpana anwi̠ny bho̠ ko okula̠n (o̠ze̠) d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠kpana anwi̠ny Isre̠l.  
\v 29 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠wo̠l d̠a̠ Abadi̠ Ododo bho̠ iten d̠a̠ egbolom a̠de, ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ a̠nwunom Izipt iwia̠n oten ani̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠an.  
\v 30 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ re̠b̠agh Aze̠riko imel wa̠leghemeni od̠ua̠l a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, ma̠ igiel bho̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham bho̠ irile igir bho̠.  
\v 31 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ sa̠ Arehab od̠eme̠ma bho̠ ada ma̠ ogbo ipoiny bho̠ a̠bhin, ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, u̠b̠aram ani̠ d̠o̠ i̠na ogigh igiel bho̠ ukunugi ma̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠da d̠o̠ awa ebhin na̠ ekima̠ bho̠.  
\v 32 Ipa̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ agba d̠a̠ i̠nye̠n od̠i ke̠re̠? Ya̠a̠, ami̠ ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠gba o̠si̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠gidio̠n, na̠ Abarak, na̠ Asamsi̠n, na̠ Aze̠fta, na̠ A̠devidi, na̠ Asamu̠e̠l, na̠ a̠riwil bho̠.  
\v 33 Awa ibhin d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ e̠ne̠gi̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ra̠dema (rebhugh), sa̠ irileghom a̠nwunom d̠a̠ igielake̠, sa̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ugua̠n bho̠, sa̠ ikpegi ma̠ aru̠nu̠ ta̠ rodughunub̠agu̠,  
\v 34 sa̠ id̠imigi ma̠ ibom re̠ba anya, sa̠ imiza̠n d̠a̠ ra̠nem a̠rigidi e̠gham (ralapogidi). Awa edugh, ya̠a̠ utenemeni awa ma̠ imoma̠na̠n e̠gham ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon okunugi ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien.  
\v 35 Ub̠egion ogbo etula̠n idi anwani̠ d̠a̠ omugh. Sa̠ ugbikimeni ma̠ idi a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n. Ipa̠n ogbo sa̠ igin agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ otenemeni awa d̠a̠ a̠d̠ugh, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ awa ibhin a̠bin wa̠ ta̠ omugh sa̠ awa ta̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠.  
\v 36 Ipa̠n ogbo sa̠ usorogiom adi̠e̠l (u̠ki̠ri̠), sa̠ u̠gu̠ro̠gh, sa̠ usobh ase̠ ugboloma̠, idi sa̠ u̠du̠o̠m rikoli, idi sa̠ u̠du̠o̠m d̠a̠ a̠rutu ikoli.  
\v 37 Idi awa sa̠ urobhod̠i ugigh, idi ogbo sa̠ ugbodo i̠wal i̠wal, idi sa̠ ubhin ogidi e̠gham (alapogidi) ugigh. Idi awa i̠lo̠gi̠an ikpora̠n a̠ruzu o̠na̠na na̠ ikpora̠n a̠ruzu iwel, sa̠ i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ esi eten esi, sa̠ ugbikimeni awa,  
\v 38 sa̠ iten ogbo ya̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ orugh d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠. Awa i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ esi eten esi d̠a̠ ra̠de i̠si̠sar (re̠ghana), na̠ d̠a̠ rigu, na̠ d̠a̠ iyol igu, na̠ d̠a̠ iyol d̠a̠ a̠de (d̠a̠ ro̠nu̠ d̠a̠ a̠de).  
\v 39 Eb̠la̠ awa ed̠igh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ologi d̠a̠ ebula̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa, ku̠ku̠m eka̠, awa i̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ ugua̠n bho̠.  
\v 40 Ezin bho̠, A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠guri ma̠ abar ola̠ a̠d̠igh asu̠wo̠ a̠pu a̠sisa̠n i̠yar. I̠na na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh d̠o̠ awa ma̠ od̠ia̠ o̠te̠i̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ bho̠ ma̠ igiel i̠yar o̠ro̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala bho̠. 
\c 12  
\p  
\v 1 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠bhon i̠yar o̠ru̠ru̠an ogboloma̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠ye̠ ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ ronyob̠a̠ a̠ma̠rugh ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠, o̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠ osorogi ma̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠dol ya̠ na̠ e̠mu̠mo̠ro̠me̠ni̠ i̠yar bho̠, okunukun i̠karabh ya̠ na̠ e̠bhad̠i̠ i̠yar onyen bho̠. Id̠ighi obhin d̠a̠ a̠ma̠ne oghil eghil wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠bho a̠mutiom d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠i̠yar bho̠.  
\v 2 Akpe̠ i̠yar ogbi ma̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠i̠yar okpon A̠zizo̠s wa̠ a̠bho ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ a̠mutiom sa̠ a̠rugh akpe̠re̠me̠ni̠ bho̠. I̠na a̠ne ma̠ a̠ma̠ne a̠d̠igh ari̠ghe̠l sa̠ a̠gbika̠ d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren, ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠loghom ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠bhon ologi a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ogir wa̠ i̠na a̠gir bho̠. I̠se̠n i̠na od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agba ukpo ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\s1 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ agu̠r anwi̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ i̠zagba (Ologi d̠inyin akpo̠ ya̠ odugh d̠o̠  //  ma̠ igiel inyin na̠ owia̠n i̠karabh) 
\r (Iburu 12:3-6) 
\p  
\v 3 I̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an egboloma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien egbika̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠ne d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin na̠ rologi d̠inyin ko odugh d̠o̠. 
\p  
\v 4 Inyin na̠ owia̠n agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ko ogir d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh, ya̠a̠ inyin ta̠ orugh d̠o̠ o̠te̠i̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ na̠ ogigh inyin ebula̠ o̠ku̠a.  
\v 5 O̠ku̠a ka̠ inyin na̠ oweleta̠n a̠kikiom wa̠ ubhin u̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin agu̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ na̠ a̠kikiom o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠? Agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, ko obhin a̠kikiom ikighom (agu̠o̠ i̠zagba) ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠ a̠degh, sa̠ ko o̠ku̠nu̠ (ologi d̠oyom odugh d̠o̠) ma̠ igiel i̠na na̠ agu̠r anwa ma̠ i̠zagba, 
\q1  
\v 6 ezin bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠kikiom (agu̠r i̠zagba) ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠na a̠tula̠n bho̠, sa̠ na̠ amar na̠ agam na̠ a̠nigha̠ ko̠nyi̠ ko̠nyi̠ ola̠ i̠na na̠ ada a̠bhin.” 
\p  
\v 7 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ atu̠n o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin na̠ abho̠ro̠gh inyin one a̠ma̠ne, ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rughom inyin agu̠o̠ anwi̠ny d̠o̠yo̠. O̠ken o̠we̠de̠ wa̠ ko okikiom d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠kighom bho̠?  
\v 8 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ inyin ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠kikiom ikighom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠kikiom na̠ a̠kighom eb̠la̠ anwi̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ iyeyi bho̠, sa̠ i̠nyin obhobho i̠kpo̠ anwi̠ny, o̠ku̠a sa̠ inyin anwi̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 9 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠, ro̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom na̠ ekikiom i̠yar na̠ ekighom, sa̠ i̠yar na̠ ozuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi na̠ onigha̠ awa ma̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, obhin d̠a̠ onyen ologi o̠da ma̠ a̠kikiom ikighom ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ opeleni ma̠ o̠ku̠a od̠um.  
\v 10 Ro̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar ekikiom i̠yar ekighom ekud̠i obhel ku̠ku̠m. Awa ibhin agu̠o̠ a̠bhon d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa egir o̠ku̠a, ya̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠kikiom i̠yar na̠ a̠kighom ma̠ i̠yar o̠te̠i̠ asu̠wo̠ wa̠ od̠ed̠ia̠n o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.  
\v 11 Agu̠o̠ i̠zagba ola̠ ame̠me̠m o̠pu̠r igiel bho̠ bo̠, a̠ten o̠ro̠ agu̠o̠ abar i̠ku̠nu̠. Ya̠a̠, ka̠ a̠tepa̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠mum imuma̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala na̠ ekima̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ u̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 12 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠kpe̠re̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ idudugha̠n aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠inyin na̠ i̠kpo̠kpu̠an-kpo̠kpu̠an asu̠kpu̠lo̠m d̠inyin.  
\v 13 Reten a̠sike d̠inyin esel, b̠o̠ka̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ edugh bho̠ na̠ a̠rukula̠ bho̠ imel e̠d̠u̠a, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ awa ta̠ e̠kpo̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu.  
\v 14 Iwia̠ne ma̠ erugha̠n eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom d̠a̠ ekima̠, ma̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ezin bho̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue abi̠gh Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ bo̠, a̠ten ka̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ab̠ab̠ala.  
\v 15 Iwia̠ne ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ko omel d̠o̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ igurumia̠n ologi ko omite d̠o̠ a̠soroni ma̠ akpe̠ sa̠ ta̠ awo̠l i̠se̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo.  
\v 16 O̠ni̠ ko oma̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ od̠e e̠ma, bo̠d̠o̠ orugh ado̠l i̠te̠i̠ agu̠o̠ I̠so̠, wa̠ a̠bhin e̠kpa ed̠ia̠n a̠dinom e̠no̠gho̠man o̠kpana o̠nyi̠ wa̠ i̠na aro̠ bho̠ (wa̠ a̠wol a̠dila̠de o̠kpana o̠nyi̠ ma̠ e̠kpa ed̠ia̠n bho̠).  
\v 17 Obhel a̠ten, ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin uloghom bho̠, bha̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ e̠no̠gho̠man o̠kpana o̠nyi̠ wa̠ i̠na aro̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ ughel i̠na. Eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ ed̠i a̠puru ma̠ e̠no̠gho̠man bho̠ eka̠, i̠na na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ onwe abar wa̠ i̠na a̠gir bho̠.  
\v 18 Inyin uru d̠o̠ d̠a̠ esi ola̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ Igu Asai̠nai̠ wa̠ ta̠ orue o̠bi̠gh okula̠n bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ e̠ba anya, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh ola̠ na̠ a̠lo, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠sai̠ (obom o̠fe̠gu̠),  
\v 19 bo̠d̠o̠ oghur od̠od̠ue, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ okoroko ola̠ na̠ agba ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠ na̠ e̠le̠gh agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ osobh asu̠gbagba ya̠ na̠ o̠gba na̠ onigha̠ awa bho̠,  
\v 20 ezin bho̠ awa irue d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir agu̠o̠ u̠to̠ unigha̠ awa bho̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “E̠nam ka̠ a̠kula̠n igu bho̠ eka̠, bha̠ irobhod̠i ma̠ egigh.” 
\p  
\v 21 Abar bho̠ a̠d̠igh a̠rugugu ka̠ ate̠i̠ esi ola̠ A̠mozizi a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin igiri ma̠ ebla̠ a̠rugugu.”  
\v 22 Ya̠a̠, inyin na̠ uru d̠a̠ Igu A̠zio̠n, obom e̠ma ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ote̠nany bho̠. Inyin na̠ oru d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ ta̠ ibom ro̠lo̠gh itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 23 Inyin na̠ oru d̠a̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n i̠kpana anwi̠ny ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ogbo ya̠ na̠ o̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠. Inyin na̠ oru d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠sobh o̠kpe̠ na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠. Inyin na̠ oru d̠a̠ aru̠mu̠gh ogbo ya̠ i̠b̠ab̠ala, sa̠ na̠ eten i̠b̠ab̠alab̠ab̠ala ma̠ i̠se̠n e̠mado̠n bho̠.  
\v 24 Inyin na̠ oru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s, wa̠ na̠ amara ma̠ enie d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io omom i̠zo̠ bho̠ na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ asi̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠zu bho̠, ya̠ id̠igh asu̠wo̠ ipu ma̠ ekekuwa̠ (ed̠i) ta̠ Ebe̠l bho̠.  
\v 25 Ikpona̠ b̠o̠ka̠ inyin ughel o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ agba ma̠ i̠d̠i̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin bho̠. Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ awa imiza̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ igiel bho̠ awa ighel i̠na wa̠ anyagh ra̠to d̠awa ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠de onon bho̠, a̠dina̠mu i̠yar, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠yar oghil o̠d̠u̠a d̠o̠yo̠, wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nany na̠ a̠bhin aghi̠m na̠ a̠kikiom i̠yar bho̠.  
\v 26 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, okoroko d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nyegi ma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n, i̠na na̠ agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠nyegi epa̠ ma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, ab̠aram na̠ e̠nai̠ny bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 27 Onon (omula̠ onyegi epa̠) na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ ta̠ od̠ur eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠le̠m bho̠ o̠si̠ghe̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ko orue d̠o̠ ed̠ura̠n bho̠ e̠ri̠la.  
\v 28 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠te̠i̠ ani̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom (a̠de onwuna̠ e̠ma) wa̠ ko onwegia̠n d̠o̠ bho̠. Id̠ighi obhin d̠a̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu igielake̠ na̠ a̠rugugu o̠ko̠l i̠na d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ ed̠igh i̠na ma̠ ologi bho̠.  
\v 29 Ezin bho̠, A̠zib̠a̠ d̠i̠yar anya ola̠ na̠ a̠d̠e na̠ a̠kunugi. 
\c 13  
\p  
\v 1 Odi aro̠ ma̠ otula̠n otula̠n odi ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ ya̠ onin ologi ima̠ra̠ (id̠umom) bho̠.  
\v 2 O̠ni̠ ko o̠we̠le̠man ma̠ o̠da isuloma̠ obhin, ezin bho̠, idi a̠nwunom na̠ e̠da ma̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ebhin ya̠a̠ iloghoma̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ oku̠a.  
\v 3 I̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ ikoli bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ agu̠b̠an ka̠ inyin od̠i na̠ awa d̠a̠ ikoli bho̠. I̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ nyen ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠bi̠gh ali̠gam a̠ruzu bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ agu̠b̠an ka̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh ani̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ali̠gam a̠ruzu d̠awa.  
\v 4 Ilom abar ola̠ akpe̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ma̠ obu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ (obhin o̠tu̠o̠m abar), sa̠ akpe̠ ma̠ a̠siwolom na̠ a̠nwani̠ d̠awa ma̠ obhin odi od̠ia̠n i̠zo̠. Ezin bho̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠bhumeni ma̠ rod̠eme̠ma ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ilom na iya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ilom.  
\v 5 Irughe ma̠ ra̠ghud̠um d̠inyin eguri ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ko oba̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ okpoki, ya̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin unwuna̠ bho̠ elegha̠n inyin, ezin bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Bebina̠ obhel ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠man anwa bo̠; ami̠ ko oghel/ogin d̠o̠ na̠ oghel/ogin anwa nyen.”  
\v 6 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠yar na̠ o̠kpo̠ ma̠ ologi na̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ i̠na wa̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠; ami̠ ko oghil d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠rugugu. O̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠gir ere a̠gboloma̠ ami̠?”  
\v 7 I̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ igba̠iny ogbo irileghom d̠inyin ya̠ i̠gba ma̠ a̠duom/o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ inigha̠ inyin bho̠. I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpon ed̠ighom d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠awa na̠ agu̠o̠ ibhin ikunugiom bho̠, ma̠ e̠ta ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa.  
\v 8 A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st onin bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegien a̠ten bho̠, wa̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠didon, na̠ wa̠ ta̠ aro̠ tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul bho̠.  
\v 9 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠d̠ien kere kere na̠ irorua̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni ogelemeni d̠o̠ inyin. A̠limon a̠luzu ma̠ o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ o̠te̠i̠ o̠ni̠, a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ obhin ed̠ia̠n ob̠em ologi. Ed̠ia̠n i̠ye̠ id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ asu̠o̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠e bho̠.  
\v 10 I̠yar unwuna̠ ma̠ enwen ola̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ egir d̠a̠ Otu-akpu̠ru̠ bho̠ eka̠ (rob̠a̠ra̠motu Otu-akpu̠ru̠ bho̠ eka̠) onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠limon o̠te̠i̠ asu̠o̠ i̠ko̠l bho̠.  
\v 11 We̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ a̠bhin asi̠ i̠nam na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ A̠lukpesi Obom E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠ obhin o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠ i̠karabh, ya̠a̠ na̠ omite d̠a̠ esi a̠kokod̠ia̠n (d̠a̠ otu-akpu̠ru̠) bho̠ na̠ o̠bhu̠gi̠ ma̠ rozu i̠nam bho̠ d̠a̠ etire.  
\v 12 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ubhin A̠zizo̠s umutiom d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ogigo e̠ma bho̠ ka̠ ugbikimeni d̠a̠ etire, b̠o̠ka̠ a̠nwunom e̠wo̠l d̠a̠ asi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala.  
\v 13 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, id̠ighi omite d̠a̠ otu-akpu̠ru̠ bho̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠na d̠a̠ etire, ma̠ i̠yar ogbika̠ ani̠ a̠d̠ien egbika̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠gbika̠ bho̠.  
\v 14 Ezin bho̠, i̠se̠n i̠yar unwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠ma ola̠ ta̠ aro̠ tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul, ya̠a̠ i̠yar na̠ ogon ema̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a ma̠ oru.  
\v 15 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, id̠ighi o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zizo̠s o̠kpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ itutumeni onigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ kigiel kigiel.  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠ ko o̠we̠le̠man o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom na̠ anwa ma̠ onigha̠ (o̠ru̠gi̠) gha̠n awa i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa i̠te̠i̠. Ogir o̠ku̠a bha̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ abar alu̠kpe̠ ola̠ a̠d̠igh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ologi.  
\v 17 I̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erileghom inyin bho̠, ma̠ egir i̠di̠ar ya̠ awa na̠ o̠to̠ bho̠. Ezin bho̠ awa na̠ ekponom inyin sa̠ ta̠ e̠gba ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa igir enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ko ogurumeni ma̠ rologi b̠o̠ka̠ awa ebhin d̠a̠ a̠libhon ologi egir ogir d̠awa, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ogir na̠ ighunuma̠ sa̠ ko omutiom d̠o̠ ma̠ asu̠wo̠ enigha̠ inyin.  
\v 18 Isiseinye ma̠ enigha̠ i̠yar, ezin bho̠ i̠yar uma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ i̠walama d̠i̠yar ib̠eb̠i sa̠ na̠ ebhir i̠yar orugh ado̠l igielake̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar (re̠kal).  
\v 19 Abar wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu bho̠ bha̠, isiseinye ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ anu̠r a̠ru ra̠ a̠zua̠n inyin (a̠d̠igh na̠ inyin aro̠).  
\v 20 A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ekima̠ bho̠ a̠b̠eton Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ omugh. I̠se̠n bha̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ Obom Okponom Ro̠na̠na ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin asi̠ bho̠ a̠d̠ia̠n i̠zo̠ wa̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ bho̠ na̠ ro̠nana d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 21 Ami̠ na̠ a̠siseiny agu̠o̠ ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ ebhir inyin ogir ya̠ igielake̠ kigiel kigiel. A̠zizo̠s alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ogir ya̠ i̠kpe̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Isosorogia̠n e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st tu̠tu̠n ka̠ od̠ua̠l id̠ud̠ul. Aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a.  
\v 22 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠ ya̠ onin ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠siseiny inyin o̠nagha a̠kikiom ya̠ ami̠ ibhin d̠a̠ a̠lebh na̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin bho̠.  
\v 23 Iloghome ma̠ na̠ omutiom A̠timoti d̠a̠ ikoli. D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ ko obia̠ d̠o̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠misi ma̠ i̠se̠n, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ami̠ ra̠ a̠zua̠n inyin.  
\v 24 Ipura̠ne ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ d̠inyin na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ iyed̠i. A̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ebhugh Ita̠li (Itili) bho̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠ ami̠ ipura̠n inyin.  
\v 25 E̠ne̠ghe̠ (Igbirigbir) ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ inyin.